data.description: Opportunity Knocks in Estrella Mountain Ranch. Don't miss this chance to own this beautiful single level home. It offers an updated kitchen overlooking the beautiful backyard, with granite counters, island, walk-in pantry & stainless steel appliances, including a gas range & wall oven and microwave. Three bedrooms, primary suite & two large bedrooms plus a flex room. Primary suite features an oversized bedroom, huge walk-in closet with extra storage and bathroom with dual vanities and separate shower & tub. There is an extended paver patio to a circular seating area, pergola, low maintenance artificial turf, and fruit trees. 3 car tandem garage provides lots of storage & workspace. Solar system is just $80 per month. This one will not disappoint.
